<% content_for :banner do %>
	<%= image_tag('verisk/banners/nucleus_banner.png') %>
	<%= demo %>
<% end %>

<div id="nucleus">
	<%# Screenshot / Elements %>
	<div id="elements" class="full_row">
		<div class="column_2">
			<header class='main'>
				An Atomic Change.
			</header>
			<p>Our approach was simple: create the ultimate user experience. Simplify graphs, create interactive charts, increase user productivity – all without sacrificing the most robust database and analytically advanced platform available for fighting fraud. We’re happy with the results, and quite sure with an ROI as high as 9:1, you will be as well. </p>
			<%= image_tag("verisk/nucleus_screens.png", :id => "nucleus_screens") %>
		</div>
		<div class="column_2">
			<header class='main'>
				Be in your element.
			</header>
			<ul id="element_boxes">
				<li>
					<header class='element_header nucleus_green'><span></span> [Pay] in your element</header>
					<p>Fight fraud on two fronts. With Nucleus you get the world’s foremost payment integrity application and Verisk Health’s signature clinical validation process. Working together in perfect harmony.</p>
				</li>
				<li>
					<header class='element_header nucleus_blue'><span></span> [Work] in your element</header>
					<p>Smarter is better. Work with Nucleus and you’ll quickly find that our idea-driven solutions, customizable interface and forward-thinking technology will help you work smarter and faster.</p>
				</li>
				<li>
					<header class='element_header nucleus_red'><span></span> [Lead] in your element</header>
					<p>ROI is king. Nucleus gives you better FWA results, leadership-level reports and accelerated productivity with its user-optimized interface. We outdid ourselves to help you outdo the competition.</p>
				</li>
				<li>
					<header class='element_header nucleus_orange'><span></span> [Thrive] in your element</header>
					<p>We built it better: Top-notch security, scalable architecture and real-time claims processing. All on a platform that plays nice with other technology. Everything clicks when you’re in your element.</p>
				</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</div>

	<%# Grid %>
	<div id="grid">
	  <div class="inner_grid">
	    <div class="grid_box left_side_box odd_row">
	      <div class="grid_image bene1"></div>
	      <div class="grid_content_wrap">      
	        <h3>Free Data Analysis, Free Reports.</h3>
	        <p>We know we can help you. Sign up for a free 
	        trial and we’ll let you test-drive the system, 
	        and quantify just how much you can save.</p>
	      </div>
	    </div>
	    <div class="grid_box right_side_box odd_row">
	      <div class="grid_image bene2"></div>
	      <div class="grid_content_wrap">      
	        <h3>Clinical Validation = Better Results.</h3>
	        <p>Only Verisk Health provides clinical validation on suspect 
	        claims by licensed clinicians (RN, MD, DDS, etc.)
	        You get fewer false positives and better results.</p>
	      </div>
	    </div>
	    <div class="grid_box left_side_box even_row">
	      <div class="grid_image bene3"></div>
	      <div class="grid_content_wrap">      
	        <h3>Prepayment Saves Time, Money.</h3>
	        <p>Each Verisk Health SaaS solution lives in a prepayment,
	        post-adjudication environment. Why? Because 
	        &#8220;pay and chase&#8221; can waste time and money.</p>
	      </div>
	    </div>
	    <div class="grid_box right_side_box even_row">
	      <div class="grid_image bene4"></div>
	      <div class="grid_content_wrap">      
	        <h3>Total Customization, Satisfaction.</h3>
	        <p>No two payors are the same. Our solutions 
	        allow you to customize nearly every aspect.  
	        This gives you greater control and happiness.</p>
	      </div>
	    </div>
	    <div class="grid_box left_side_box odd_row">
	      <div class="grid_image bene5"></div>
	      <div class="grid_content_wrap">      
	        <h3>On-Demand Reports, Information.</h3>
	        <p>Create and schedule custom or preset reports 
	        with our On-Demand reporting module. You  
	        get instant information and instant satisfaction.</p>
	      </div>
	    </div>
	    <div class="grid_box right_side_box odd_row">
	      <div class="grid_image bene6"></div>
	      <div class="grid_content_wrap">      
	        <h3>Dashboards, KPIs Drive Success.</h3>
	        <p>Our customizable roles-based dashboards 
	        display KPIs, alerts and more. View savings, 
	        claims and other critical information real-time.</p>
	      </div>
	    </div>
	    <%= clear %>
	  </div>
	</div>

	<%= render :partial => "payment_accuracy/service_links" %> 

</div>